1. Chronological CV (Classic / Traditional)

Layout & Design

Clean, formal, single-column

Work experience listed from most recent to oldest

Minimal colors (black, gray, navy)

Best for

Corporate roles

Finance, Accounting

Administration

Government jobs

Education

Why it works

Shows career progression clearly

Preferred by recruiters and ATS systems

2. Functional CV (Skills-Based)

Layout & Design

Skills and competencies at the top

Less focus on dates

Simple but flexible layout

Best for

Career changers

People with employment gaps

Freelancers

Entry-level candidates

Why it works

Highlights abilities over job history

3. Combination (Hybrid) CV

Layout & Design

Skills summary at the top

Chronological experience below

Balanced, modern structure

Best for

IT professionals

Project managers

Engineers

Mid-level professionals

Why it works

Shows both skills and experience equally

4. Creative CV

Layout & Design

Unique typography

Color accents

Icons, graphics, custom sections

Often two-column

Best for

Graphic designers

UI/UX designers

Marketing professionals

Content creators

Why it works

Demonstrates creativity visually

5. Minimalist CV

Layout & Design

White space

Simple fonts

Very clean and elegant

No graphics or icons

Best for

Consultants

Lawyers

Executives

Academics

Why it works

Looks professional and easy to read

6. Modern Professional CV

Layout & Design

Two-column layout

Subtle colors

Icons for sections

Skill bars or ratings

Best for

Business analysts

HR professionals

Sales managers

Operations roles

Why it works

Contemporary but still professional

7. Technical CV

Layout & Design

Structured sections

Tables or bullet-heavy layouts

Emphasis on tools and technologies

Best for

Software developers

Data scientists

Engineers

Cybersecurity professionals

Why it works

Clearly shows technical expertise

8. Academic CV

Layout & Design

Long-form (2–6+ pages)

Dense text

Formal formatting

Best for

Professors

Researchers

PhD candidates

Scientists

Why it works

Includes publications, research, teaching experience



10. Executive CV

Layout & Design

Premium, elegant design

Strong personal branding

Leadership-focused sections

Best for

CEOs

Directors

Senior managers

Board-level roles

Why it works

Emphasizes impact, leadership, and strategy

11. One-Page CV

Layout & Design

Ultra-compact

Prioritized content

Clean typography

Best for

Students

Fresh graduates

Internships

Junior roles

Why it works

Quick to scan, recruiter-friendly

12. International CV

Layout & Design

Country-specific formatting

Photo included (EU/Asia)

Personal details section

Best for

Overseas jobs

Multinational companies

Why it works

Matches global hiring standards

13. Portfolio CV

Layout & Design

Links to work samples

QR codes

Visual project sections

Best for

Architects

Designers

Writers

Photographers

Why it works

Shows real work, not just claims



















